# Lawrence Cook

## Senior Administrative Associate Center Operations and Administration

Email: **[lcook@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:lcook@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Lawrence is going into his 16th year as a UT employee, spending 12+ with Parking and Transportation Services & 3+ with Office of Graduate Admissions, formerly GIAC Graduate and International Admissions Center and is very excited to become a member of the TACC – Texas Advanced Computing Center as a Senior Administrative Associate.

### Memberships

* UT Staff Council Member & Chair of the Parking and Transportation Committee: 2008 – 2010
* Elgin ISD District Advisory Committee Member 2018 / 2019 - 2019 /2020
* Elgin ISD Citizens Bond Committee Member: 2023 - 2024

